# Title: Arbitrary File Download Via MSPUB.EXE
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-08-19
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects usage of "MSPUB" (Microsoft Publisher) to download arbitrary files
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.stealth, attack.t1218
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_mspub_download.yml

CommandLine IN ("*ftp://*", "*http://*", "*https://*") Image="*\\MSPUB.exe" OR OriginalFileName="MSPUB.exe"